            "type": "sequence-step",
            "pid": "38"
        },
        "45": {
            "data": "点按“抹掉AppleWatch”。选择“下一步”，直到抹掉设备上的数据。",
            "type": "sequence-step",
            "pid": "38"
        },
        "46": {
            "data": "点按您的AppleWatch旁边的移除按钮。",
            "type": "sequence-step",
            "pid": "38"
        },
        "48": {
            "data": "则表示激活锁已打开。",
            "type": "solution",
